{{nihongo|'''''Jaseiken Necromancer'''''|{{ruby|邪聖剣|じゃせいけん}}ネクロマンサー}} is a 1988 [[role-playing video game]] by [[Hudson Soft]] for the [[PC Engine]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/jaseiken-necromancer|title=Jaseiken Necromancer for TurboGrafx-16 (1988) - MobyGames|website=MobyGames|accessdate=27 July 2018}}</ref> The game has never been officially translated into English despite becoming available as a downloadable purchase in United States and Europe.

A sequel, ''Necromancer 2'', was released on mobile devices in Japan. It was ported to the [[Nintendo DSi]] as '''''Jaseiken Necromancer: Nightmare Reborn''''' in 2010.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.konami.com/games/jp/ja/products/dl_dsi_necromancer/|title=邪聖剣ネクロマンサー NIGHTMARE REBORN - KONAMI コナミ製品・サービス情報サイト|website=KONAMI コナミ製品・サービス情報サイト|accessdate=27 July 2018}}</ref>

==Re-releases==
On December 2, 2006, ''Jaseiken Necromancer'' saw its first release on the [[Nintendo Wii]] [[Virtual Console]] in Japan.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.konami.com/games/jp/ja/products/dl_wii_necromancer_vc/ |title=邪聖剣ネクロマンサー &#124; Konami コナミ製品・サービス情報サイト |access-date=2018-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318000306/https://www.konami.com/games/jp/ja/products/dl_wii_necromancer_vc/ |archive-date=2017-03-18 |url-status=dead}}</ref>

On December 16, 2009, the game was re-released for the [[PlayStation 3]] and [[PlayStation Portable]], available only on [[PlayStation Network]] in Japan.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.konami.com/games/jp/ja/products/dl_pspps3vita_necromancer_arch/ |title=邪聖剣ネクロマンサー &#124; Konami コナミ製品・サービス情報サイト |access-date=2018-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317144412/https://www.konami.com/games/jp/ja/products/dl_pspps3vita_necromancer_arch/ |archive-date=2017-03-17 |url-status=dead}}</ref>

In February 2011, the game was released as ''Necromancer'' on [[Apple Inc.|Apple]]'s [[App Store (iOS)|App Store]], but is no longer available to purchase.

In March 2017, the game was released in Japan on the [[Nintendo Wii U]] Virtual Console.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/titles/20010000026190|title=邪聖剣ネクロマンサー - Wii U - 任天堂|publisher=|accessdate=27 July 2018}}</ref> In February 2018 it was added to the United States and Europe eShops in original untranslated form, the first time the game was available for purchase outside of Japan.

In 2020, the game was released as one of the 57 games included in the international release of the [[TurboGrafx-16 Mini]].<ref>{{cite web |last1=McWhertor |first1=Michael |title=Konami confirms seven more games for TurboGrafx-16 mini |url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/8/8/20791763/turbografx-16-mini-games-list-pc-engine-konami |website=Polygon |access-date=28 March 2021 |language=en |date=8 August 2019}}</ref>

